tor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon icon-envelope2\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Contact<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1a04a2d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1a04a2d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-73eb6eb\" data-id=\"73eb6eb\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac855f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ac855f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A proud native of Austin and a graduate of the University of Texas at Austin, Christine Choate has built an exceptional career spanning over 32 years in real estate. Her expertise extends across all facets of the industry, from personal investments to brokerage leadership.<\/p><p>Christine has personally bought, sold, constructed, and renovated properties throughout Central Texas, managing over $22 million in personal investment transactions. Her keen eye for opportunities and deep market knowledge have been instrumental in her success.<\/p><p>As the founder and owner of Horizon Realty, Christine has led one of the most respected real estate firms in Central Texas for 26 years. Horizon Realty, home to approximately 100 professional Realtors, has been a trusted partner for buyers, sellers, and investors since 1999. The firm offers comprehensive services, including residential and commercial sales, leasing, and property management, while maintaining strong relationships with title companies, mortgage lenders, inspectors, appraisers, surveyors, and contractors.<\/p><p>Horizon Realty stands out in the industry by offering one of the most competitive commission structures in Central Texas, unparalleled agent support, and a culture that fosters both professional growth and a sense of family. As a result, Horizon Realty has consistently outperformed market standards, generating hundreds of millions of dollars in real estate sales.<\/p><p>Beyond business, Christine is passionate about giving back to the community. Horizon Realty actively supports Coats for Kids, Soles for Souls, The Miracle Foundation, the Capital Area Food Bank, Dress for Success, Toys for Tots, and Austin Pets Alive.<\/p><p>Christine is also a dedicated leader in the real estate industry. She has been an active member of the Women\u2019s Council of Realtors, Real Estate Council of Austin, and Texas Real Estate Political Action Committee. She has served on the Nominating Committee and Governmental Affairs Committee for the Austin Board of Realtors and has shared her expertise through presentations at the Austin Institute of Real Estate, the Austin Board of Realtors, and the University of Texas at Austin.<\/p><p>While continuing to expand her real estate portfolio and lead her brokerage, Christine enjoys spending time with her family, their whippet, and making the most of her newly built pickleball court!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac11626 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"ac11626\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-ty